name: Stormtrooper (V)
Lore: 'One of the countless elite shock troops totally loyal to the Emperor. Unquestioningly follows orders. Willing to sacrifice their lives to accomplish a mission. First-strike force.',
Text: 'When drawn for weapon or battle destiny, destiny +2. While present at a site and armed with a blaster rifle, forfeit +2 and draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise.',
